      "text": "The purpose of the business is to create technical, social and governance tools that enable cooperative businesses to exchange value and engage in coproductions which are currently difficult to achieve, complex to negotiate, and lack clear legal frameworks and incentive structures that would enable such cooperations to scale and produce useful products and services."
