      "text": "*The purpose of the business is to offer to co-operatives and freelancers affordable access to a range of services which it would either be impossible or prohibitive for them to use - on both technical and financial grounds.*\n*Such services would range from access to digital assets and tools, to business support services, to sophisticated digital infrastructure.*\n*The primary mode through which members access the services and engage with each other is through participation in a three-tiered suite of complementary currencies.*\n*This engagement benefits and strengthens the co-operative's members by reducing their reliance on hard currency - thus increasing their profitability and resilience. It offers access to a counter-cyclical mechanism of exchange.*\n"
    },
